content:
This is my end-to-end developed data product during my first full-time job, aiming to guide toB &amp; toC marketing for our novel new energy brand Weltmeister. The landing version with platform adaptation and UI improvement had been delivered successfully and worked well.
1. Product Description Completed work:
Construction of city ranking system, you can see the overall ranking: top10, top30, top50, top100 Complete data aggregation and indicator system construction for 306 cities With the city panel display tool, you can observe the performance of each city on well-designed indicator factors and specific factor items, including: Overall auto market;
Brand potential;
Basic urban development;
Traffic and purchase restriction policies;
Dealer channels
Follow-up:
For the existing toC city marketing panel, use the final data results to form a feedback mechanism to increase the richness of indicators and the usability of tools. An evaluation system for toB&rsquo;s overall sales potential from a large customer perspective. With sales execution as the goal, refine the direct help of the data results in front of sales execution, including: Assessment of user concentration at the community level and assessment of the completeness of basic charging facilities;
Sorting out the global new energy vehicle owner labeling system to answer who the new energy users are in different cities and what kind of cars they need;
Large customer loss analysis tool
2. Access Requirements This tool uses a browser as the display and analysis platform, and requires the use of Chrome/Safari/Opera/Firefox/IE (&gt;= 11.0) and other browsers that support HTML5. Since the displayed platform will need to load online map resources in the future, it needs to be browsed on a PC with a network environment. It is recommended to use a resolution &gt;1024*768.
3. User Instructions Detailed Manual

